Cell["\<\
addFirstMonomer initializes the global lists by specifying a first monomer. \
Adds the coordinates, chem bonds and itp information to global lists.
Requires a pdb and itp file imported as a table.\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.883237747079797*^9, 3.883237792540896*^9}, {
   3.883747239793157*^9, 3.883747303622965*^9}, {3.883747353571352*^9, 
